  "title": "Sales Executive (Manufacturing / Construction - Training Provided)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $ 3500 - $ 4500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: West (Company Transport provided)</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Normal Working Hours (Mon to Fri only)</strong></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong>\n</p><ul><li>Support the Head of Sales in daily sales activities.</li><li>Identify and follow up on potential customers and project opportunities.</li><li>Conduct customer meetings and site visits to understand requirements.</li><li>Prepare and follow up on quotations, proposals, and contracts.</li><li>Build and maintain good relationships with customers and handle enquiries.</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth project execution.</li><li>Assist with invoicing, progress claims, and payment follow-ups.</li><li>Update sales records and reports using the ERP system.</li><li>Perform other sales-related duties as assigned.\n</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree  in any field of study. Candidates without experiences are welcome to apply. </li><li>Able to read and understand architectural and structural drawings as well as AutoCAD will be an advantage.</li></ul><p><br /><br />Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the\nresume<br /></p><p></p><ul><li>Work experience and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br /></p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
